title: Tuskegee University Board of Trustees elects new chairman and officers (Tuskegee University)
text: ( Source : Tuskegee University ) TUSKEGEE, Ala. ( October 17 , 2015 ) - During its annual fall meeting this weekend, the Tuskegee University's Board of Trustees elected trustee John E. Page to serve as its chairman. He replaces retired Maj. Gen.
